The MDRRMO in close coordination with the MDRRMC be required to prepare a well-planned/studied LDRRMFIP which must also include under a separate caption, the list of projects and activities charged to the unexpended LDRRMF of previous years which must be implemented as planned in order to optimize utilization and bring the desired benefits to its constituents and to avoid future reversion of LDRMMF to the General fund. The LGU must ensure the efficient utilization o the LDRRM Fund in order that the objectives of the various programs, projects and activities funded therefrom are achieved;

